---
---

<section class="deb-section" id="debrief">
  <div class="deb-layout">
    <div class="reveal">
      <span class="sec-label">La feature principale</span>
      <h2>Ton coach <em>personnel</em> chaque dimanche soir</h2>
      <p class="sec-sub">Chaque semaine, l'IA analyse l'intégralité de tes trades, détecte ce que tu aurais du mal à voir toi-même, et te fixe 3 objectifs concrets pour la semaine suivante.</p>
      <div class="deb-points">
        <div class="deb-pt">
          <div class="deb-pt-ic" style="background:rgba(16,185,129,.1);border:1px solid rgba(16,185,129,.2)">✓</div>
          <div><div class="deb-pt-t">Résumé en langage naturel</div><div class="deb-pt-d">Pas des stats brutes — une analyse rédigée qui nomme tes vraies failles.</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="deb-pt">
          <div class="deb-pt-ic" style="background:rgba(59,130,246,.1);border:1px solid rgba(59,130,246,.2)">🎯</div>
          <div><div class="deb-pt-t">3 objectifs personnalisés</div><div class="deb-pt-d">Générés depuis tes propres patterns. Pas des conseils génériques de YouTube.</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="deb-pt">
          <div class="deb-pt-ic" style="background:rgba(139,92,246,.1);border:1px solid rgba(139,92,246,.2)">📈</div>
          <div><div class="deb-pt-t">Boucle semaine après semaine</div><div class="deb-pt-d">Les objectifs S11 deviennent le bilan de S12. Tu mesures ta progression.</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="reveal" style="transition-delay:.15s">
      <div class="deb-mock">
        <div class="dm-week">Rapport hebdomadaire — Semaine 12</div>
        <div class="dm-title">Weekly Debrief IA</div>
        <div class="dm-sub">28 trades analysés · généré dim. 23h00</div>
        <div class="dm-stats">
          <div class="dm-stat"><div class="dm-val text-g">+$1 840</div><div class="dm-lbl">P&amp;L net</div></div>
          <div class="dm-stat"><div class="dm-val text-b">67%</div><div class="dm-lbl">Win rate</div></div>
          <div class="dm-stat"><div class="dm-val">74<span style="font-size:11px;color:var(--txt3)">/100</span></div><div class="dm-lbl">Score</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="dm-ai">
          <div class="dm-ai-lbl"><div class="ai-dot-anim"></div>Analyse IA</div>
          <div class="dm-ai-txt">Tu as <strong>respecté tes stops à 100%</strong> — une première en 6 semaines. Ton talon d'Achille reste le <span class="warn">jeudi après 15h</span> : 4 trades sur 5 perdants. Si tu corriges ce seul créneau, ton win rate structurel dépasse <strong class="good">72%</strong>.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="dm-obj-title">Objectifs semaine prochaine</div>
        <div class="dm-obj"><div class="dm-obj-dot">○</div>Stopper toute activité le jeudi après 15h</div>
        <div class="dm-obj"><div class="dm-obj-dot">○</div>Max 4 trades le vendredi matin</div>
        <div class="dm-obj"><div class="dm-obj-dot">○</div>Éviter GBP/USD — 3ème semaine en perte</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .deb-section {
    background: var(--bg2);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--b);
  }

  .deb-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 56px;
    align-items: center;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .deb-points { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 18px; margin-top: 36px; }

  .deb-pt { display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: flex-start; }

  .deb-pt-ic {
    width: 36px; height: 36px;
    border-radius: 9px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 17px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .deb-pt-t { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 3px; }
  .deb-pt-d { font-size: 13px; color: var(--txt2); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.6; }

  .deb-mock {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--b2);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 24px;
    box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.5);
  }

  .dm-week { font-size: 10px; font-family: var(--mono); color: var(--txt3); letter-spacing: .8px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .dm-title { font-family: var(--disp); font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -.4px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .dm-sub { font-size: 12px; color: var(--txt3); margin-bottom: 18px; }

  .dm-stats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 18px; }

  .dm-stat { background: var(--bg3); border: 1px solid var(--b); border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px; }
  .dm-val { font-family: var(--disp); font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -.3px; }
  .dm-lbl { font-size: 10px; color: var(--txt3); font-family: var(--mono); margin-top: 3px; }
  .text-g { color: var(--green); }
  .text-b { color: var(--blue2); }

  .dm-ai { background: linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(59,130,246,.08),rgba(139,92,246,.08)); border: 1px solid rgba(139,92,246,.15); border-radius: 9px; padding: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .dm-ai-lbl { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px; font-size: 9px; font-family: var(--mono); color: var(--blue2); letter-spacing: .5px; margin-bottom: 9px; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .ai-dot-anim { width: 6px; height: 6px; background: var(--blue); border-radius: 50%; animation: blink 2s ease infinite; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .dm-ai-txt { font-size: 12px; color: var(--txt2); line-height: 1.75; }
  .dm-ai-txt strong { color: var(--txt); }
  .dm-ai-txt .warn { color: var(--yel); }
  .dm-ai-txt .good { color: var(--green); }

  .dm-obj-title { font-size: 10px; font-family: var(--mono); color: var(--txt3); letter-spacing: .7px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .dm-obj { display: flex; gap: 9px; padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(99,155,255,.06); align-items: center; font-size: 12px; color: var(--txt2); }
  .dm-obj:last-child { border: none; }
  .dm-obj-dot { color: var(--txt3); font-size: 14px; flex-shrink: 0; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .deb-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
  }
</style>
